<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226709>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 31. Eukoenenia montagudi sp. nov., holotype. 24, frontal organ, dorsal view; 25, lateral organ, dorsal view and lobe insertions; 26, deuto-tritosternal setae; 27, coxa I; 28, coxa III; 29, coxa II; 30, coxa IV; 31, pedipalp coxa. Thick coxal setae represented with a thicker line and a terminal spine. Scale bars: 24 – 26 = 50 µm; 27 – 31 = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226709/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226710>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32 – 35. Eukoenenia montagudi sp. nov., holotype. 32, basitarsi 3 – 4, leg I; 33, basitarsus, leg IV; 34, opisthosoma, ventral view; 35, female genital region. Scale bars: 32 – 33 = 100 µm; 34 = 200 µm; 35 = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226710/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

